    "body": "Thanks, that gave me some head start, will explore this route\r\n\r\nIf I create a BrowserWindow without height and width and then use HTML  , CSS  I get\r\n\r\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1934468/21909978/0a1526f2-d8cf-11e6-9b39-17a9f5336f15.png)\r\n\r\nvar circularPrefsWindow = new BrowserWindow({\r\n       transparent:true,\r\n       frame  : false\r\n   })\r\n\r\nHTML:\r\n\r\n```\r\n<body style=\"-webkit-app-region: drag\">\r\n     <div>\r\n      empty div to hold content\r\n     </div>\r\n    <script>\r\n       $(document).ready(function()\r\n       {\r\n         $(\"div\").css(\"border-radius\", \"50%\");\r\n       });\r\n    </script>\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\nCSS:\r\n\r\n```\r\n<style>\r\n      div\r\n      {\r\n          width: 50%;\r\n          height: auto;\r\n          padding-top: 50%;\r\n          background: #ababab;\r\n      }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n```"
